### Crear nova reseña
POST http://localhost:5000/api/resenas HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_reseña": "RES001",
  "id_usuario": "68f5f6accb7cf445387aa124",
  "id_pala": "68f60d9acb7cf445387aa16b",
  "comentario": "Excel·lent pala, molt còmoda i potent!",
  "puntuacion": 5
}

### ============================
### Obtenir totes les reseñas
GET http://localhost:5000/api/resenas HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================
### Obtenir reseña per ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/resenas/6909be52a56c9f7a580b8d6c HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================
### Actualitzar reseña
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/resenas/6909be52a56c9f7a580b8d6c HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comentario": "Molt bona pala, però una mica pesada després d'un temps.",
  "puntuacion": 4
}

### ============================
### Eliminar reseña
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/resenas/6909be52a56c9f7a580b8d6c HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
